00:03:44.340 --> 00:03:46.240
And it's not really
fair to group all motion

00:03:46.240 --> 00:03:48.664
into just the polish category.

00:03:48.664 --> 00:03:50.080
There are certain
levels of motion

00:03:50.080 --> 00:03:53.160
that are key components
to making a great app,

00:03:53.160 --> 00:03:56.910
and it does so much more
than just polish it.

00:03:56.910 --> 00:03:59.600
It can guide users
to the next view.

