00:04:21.980 --> 00:04:24.610
But by doing that,
all of these things

00:04:24.610 --> 00:04:28.165
together just make a feeling
of a really high quality app.

00:04:28.165 --> 00:04:29.540
And if this is
done right, you'll

00:04:29.540 --> 00:04:31.540
be left with a really
solid animation experience

00:04:31.540 --> 00:04:35.612
throughout your app
or family of apps.

00:04:35.612 --> 00:04:37.820
