00:04:43.534 --> 00:04:44.950
A lot of you
probably don't really

00:04:44.950 --> 00:04:45.970
think about this anymore.

00:04:45.970 --> 00:04:47.595
It's just opening
and closing an event.

00:04:47.595 --> 00:04:49.934
Happens all the time.

00:04:49.934 --> 00:04:52.350
But there are a lot of really
subtle things happening here

00:04:52.350 --> 00:04:54.830
to help you understand
