00:04:54.830 --> 00:04:58.760
to make sure you don't
get lost and using it.

00:04:58.760 --> 00:05:00.969
What if this didn't have
an animation at all?

00:05:00.969 --> 00:05:02.760
Without an animation
here, it's really hard

00:05:02.760 --> 00:05:05.670
to tell what was triggered,
where you ended up,

00:05:05.670 --> 00:05:07.510
and where the view
that you just left

00:05:07.510 --> 00:05:11.462
lives in relation to this
new view that's there.

00:05:11.462 --> 00:05:12.920
Loading also stands
out a lot more,

00:05:12.920 --> 00:05:16.077
because there's nothing
really there to mask it.

00:05:16.077 --> 00:05:18.160
All right, so this is a
