00:05:27.733 --> 00:05:30.270
have.

00:05:30.270 --> 00:05:32.530
Sure, it feels a little
better, but it's still not

00:05:32.530 --> 00:05:34.290
really communicating anything.

00:05:34.290 --> 00:05:36.677
The view just kind of
slides in from the bottom.

00:05:36.677 --> 00:05:38.885
There's still no relationship
between the object that

00:05:38.885 --> 00:05:40.580
was tapped and the
new view coming in.

00:05:42.784 --> 00:05:45.200
There are a lot of subtleties
in animation techniques used

00:05:45.200 --> 00:05:48.930
to get this calendar transition
to feel just smooth and right.

